@startuml state-review-lifecycle
title Review Request Lifecycle

[*] --> Submitted : Content submitted\nfor review

Submitted : Awaiting reviewer\nassignment
Submitted --> InReview : Reviewers assigned\nvia rotation

InReview : Reviewers evaluating\nagainst checklist
InReview --> Approved : All reviewers approve\n(consensus reached)
InReview --> Rejected : Any reviewer rejects
InReview --> RevisionRequested : Reviewer requests\nchanges

RevisionRequested : Creator notified\nof required changes
RevisionRequested --> Resubmitted : Creator updates\nand resubmits

Resubmitted : Previous decisions\ncleared
Resubmitted --> InReview : New reviewers\nassigned

Approved : Content ready\nfor publication
Approved --> [*]

Rejected : Feedback provided\nto creator
Rejected --> [*]

@enduml
